 2650        private string SerialiseObject(HealthIssueDetails[] oarrHealthIssueDetails)
 2651        {

 2656            {

 2658                {
 02659                    XMLserializer = new System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer(oarrHealthIssueDetails.GetType());
 02660                    XMLserializer.Serialize(stringWriter, oarrHealthIssueDetails);
 02661                    XmlString = stringWriter.ToString();
 2662                }
 2663            }
 02664            catch (Exception ex)
 2665            {
 02666                iSOFT.LORENZO.AMS.Publisher.CAMS.PublishProblemInfo(new iSOFT.LORENZO.AMS.Events.CErrorEvent(ex, 0));
 2667            }
 2668            finally
 2669            {
 02670                 if (null != stringWriter)
 02671                    stringWriter.Close();
 2672            }
